        "rendered": "<p>The Toolbar is an area of the screen just above the site that lists useful administration screen links such as add a new post or edit your profile. The Toolbar contains links to information about WordPress, as well as quick-links to create new posts, pages and links, add new users, review comments, and alerts to [&hellip;]</p>\n",
